description: This skill will give you a report on the current or forecast air quality for London. As well as general information on air quality, pollutants and weather affecting London, it will give specific information about ozone, nitrogen dioxide, sulphur dioxide, PM2.5 and PM10 particulate matter where there are expected significant concentrations of these. The report is based on data sourced from Transport for London public information feeds (this skill is not associated with Transport for London).
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask London Air Quality for the forecast
name: London Air Quality
shortDescription: Find out the current or forecast air quality conditions for London, including information on pollutants, and weather affecting these.
